values: Hey..muh friends...I'm in school, bored as hell, I will probley get in trouble for being on here but who gives a shit. I just got done with a stupid computer applications test...stupid ppl. Oh, and in gym, oooh, this really pissed me off...one of my so called friends walked up to this 10th grader and told him that I thought he was hott!! I got really mad. But, I have to go, torture someone...BYE!!

You know what I taught to someone the other day? Also, someone showed me today, that, well, its true..so now, i'll share it with you! Friends are the best Friends can make you feel warm and fuzzy inside Friends listin to your problems Friends care Friends pick you up when your down Friends do a lot for you... ...always remember, to keep them... you should always, always, return the favors they give you. kep it in mind... ~Cass

Hey Peeps,

  Today, was a loooong day...I just hope that tomarrow will go by faster. Uhhh, well, today, I went to the mall and I only spent 70.00...I was soooo proud of myself! But anyway, I came home and my grandparents were such assholes to me...But meh, anyway...I want to go see that movie Saw sooooo badley...!!!... Okay, I'm bored, bye.

OMG! Today was incredible. I was happy, then sad, then happy, then okay, then extreamly happy, then sad again, then confused, now I'm very happy, to know what I once known, but what was then forgotten. But Paulo soon made me realize, its not just about the things that I thought life was, its other things. But anyway...I no longer love anyone, just love people as good friends. One person in particular. But he, well, i'm sure you know by now who he is...but I am still keeping his identity...well, as it is. But yeah, I cried, I laughed, and now, I am good, today was a good day. But if I don't get some sleep damnit, I don't know what i'll do!

                                      Love ya!
                                          ~Cassie

Hey Guys, I'm kinda bored, I had plans, but as usual, they have been cancled...due to, uh, some awkward reasons...nvm. Anyway. Now, I am stuck here, watching "PoltergieistII: The Other Side" uh, its okay. I have nothing better to do, except try to make my journal better, am I? So, reply and tell me!!!

                               Love ya bunches and bunches!!!

                                                     ~Cassie

Uhhh, I am happy. I had the bestest of best conversations with my friends, and some of the worst of..the worst. Well, it started out with Paulo..we had a really good and, well, very interesting conversation with him...but, who wouldnt, Paulo's Paulo, and I Paulo how he is, very, himself. Then Steven, we didnt say much...Neither did me and Mellisa nor Sam, Um, come to think of it, hardly anone except for my so-called "friend" Tiffany, got I hate that bitch. That is exactly what she was being too. But hey, I'm not talking shit, I wouldnt care if she was reading this right now...Yes, Tiff, I called you a B-I-T-C-H. You expected me to buy your little routiene when you call me crying( which is...so fake, just like you). But well, I didn't. Why? BECAUSE, I DON'T BELIEVE ANYTHING YOU FUCKING SAY! And, you are a horrible friend, you never support me and ANYTHING I do. And you also, never ,ever care about anything I say, shit, I never care about your little fucking problems, but I try to listin and help you. But thats okay, I dont need you, I never did, never will. Your a bitch, not a witch, like you say. You THINK you are, but, your not. YOUR FAKE, EVERYTHING ABOUT YOU IS FAKE!!! Anyway, I'm not spending any more time on her, its a waste. I also was planning on going to the movies but you know, Johnny wouldnt go, and I didn't want to go with anyone else, well, I can't say that, because I did want to go with someone else...anyway. I am kind of tired time to go hit the coke! Later! Luv Ya! Bunches! ~Cassie~ P.S The movie "Saw" came out today, I am going to ask someone to go with me...I want to go tomarrow, so hopefully, he can go!!!

I had a very interesting coversation with a lot of people today, sooo, I am very happy...and confused, wait, maybe i'm not...
but yet I am satisfyed, I just hope other people ARE!!! I feel like crying though...people also made me very sad, my grandpa made me feel horrable. He keeps threatining to send me back up in Virginia w/my dad and step-brother...uh-oh is right...I don't want to go...
If I do, I will miss you all, and I will also wrte to everyone I know!!! I think...if you want me to...I am tired, and sad, so I am going to go now...
             Love everyone Bunches and bunches of oats
                ~Cassie***

Oh my god, I feel so horrible right now, I'm not sure if i'm hungry or sick, I think both, but anyway, we have a lot of work to do...Computer Apps. is such a gay class, I already know how to do eveything they tell me to do...Its cool though, I get to go online and do what I want!!!

   I feel kind of neglected  right now, no one is paying attention to me...    EVEN THOUGH THEY ARE RIGHT NEXT TO ME!!! GRRR!

   Well, I am going to go, I have work to do, if I don't get sick first...
                      ****
                    ~Cassie
